359
00:31:43,740 --> 00:31:45,630
A man of action.

360
00:31:45,660 --> 00:31:50,910
I knew that day you were destined
for great things, Pablo.

361
00:31:52,580 --> 00:31:55,440
- [Martinez in Spanish] Good evening.
- [men] Colonel.

362
00:31:55,460 --> 00:31:56,750
