an ignorant old man?

406
00:35:35,010 --> 00:35:36,260
That's right.

407
00:35:40,180 --> 00:35:43,230
Now tell me... [shaky chuckle]

408
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:46,070
Tell me...

409
00:35:48,070 --> 00:35:50,530
what you think of me.

410
00:35:55,120 --> 00:35:57,640
- Who cares?
- I do.

411
00:35:57,660 --> 00:35:59,350
[drops knife]

412
00:35:59,370 --> 00:36:01,410
It's important to me.

413
00:36:04,380 --> 00:36:08,460
You wanted to come live on this farm
with your wife and kids.

414
00:36:10,050 --> 00:36:12,760
But that's not possible, Pablo.

415
00:36:14,220 --> 00:36:16,680
